  "body": "### Description\n\nWith Quarkus 2+ I need to put a io.quarkus.runtime.annotations.StaticInitSafe annotation on my ConfigSource if I need static init.\r\n\r\nThis annotation is part of core though and the library that contains the ConfigSource is not only used with quarkus.\r\n\r\nYES i could add a compileOnly dependence to quarkus-code but that doesn't look right.\r\n\r\nQuarkus should have a slick stereotype only dependency for the kind of stuff that might be needed to enrich other libs in order to make them function properly with quarkus.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
